{"tid":2457884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際太空站發現未知的微生物","createTime":"2021-03-23T04:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T05:10:24.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7f38851f58c3d1511a982592be5e836455ca118b","tid":2457884,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"我們生活周遭有眾多細菌和真菌，國際太空站（ISS）的低重力環境也不例外。美國和印<br />\n度的研究人員發現 4 種 ISS 裡生長的細菌菌株，其中有 3 種是科學界完全未知。<br />\n <br />\n先前為證明生命可在太空傳播的理論，曾將異常球菌屬（Deinococcus）放在太空站外面<br />\n 3 年，結果確認某些細菌可在惡劣的太空條件下生存，但這些細菌應該是地球帶來的。<br />\n這些菌株分別在研究站的高架面板、觀察機械臂操作的穹頂艙、餐桌表面收集；第 4 個<br />\n是 2011 年返回地球的舊 HEPA 濾網發現。<br />\n <br />\n這 4 種全部屬於土壤和淡水菌株，會參與固氮、植物生長，並有助防禦植物病原體。由<br />\n於 ISS 的太空人一直有種植少量食物，所以發現與植物相關的微生物不足為奇。HEPA 濾<br />\n網細菌鑑定為已知物種，稱為羅氏甲基桿菌（Methylorubrum rhodesianum），其他三種<br />\n則為相似但未知的物種。研究團隊認為，由於這些微生物可在 ISS 的惡劣條件下生存，<br />\n因此分析菌株遺傳，可尋找用於幫助植物生長的基因。<br />\n <br />\n研究人員發現，其中一種 ISS 菌株 IF7SW-B2T 有與植物生長相關基因，基因產生的酶可<br />\n促進根和芽細胞分裂。研究人員表示，在國際太空站已收集約 1,000 個樣本，但尚未返<br />\n回地球，因此將來或許還有更大的驚奇。未來若長途跋涉前往火星，太空人將長期與數十<br />\n億種微生物相處，了解這些不同物種很重要。此發現發表在《Journal Frontiers in<br />\nMicrobiology》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2021/03/23/unknown-microbes-found-on-iss/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2021%2F03%2F23%2Funknown-microbes-found-on-iss%2F&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXEuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=38729774\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2021/03/23/unknown-microbes-found-on-iss/</a>"},{"pid":"4f777e8ffc07d128dbb5c8220ada39566ef6c77c","tid":2457884,"uid":41288,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgkYEF2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgkYEF2.jpg&h=2c38c04d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94f1b950c17d4d786b5d8a884e9beb0e9cfdeb19","tid":2457884,"uid":197563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/1-18-2017/uhG_el.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F1-18-2017%2FuhG_el.gif&h=00ed0d3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bddcd932a1ecceb0fd49a1a12aac409bca674ee1","tid":2457884,"uid":393145,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:16:05.000Z","msg":"中共: YEAH, 武肺來自國際太空站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f40b6d18250bcb33fe0527132979dc0641f653a","tid":2457884,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f777e8ffc07d128dbb5c8220ada39566ef6c77c","tid":2457884,"uid":41288,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgkYEF2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgkYEF2.jpg&h=2c38c04d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef55f0c223c27c228217ea8bd17bf2da09b259e2","tid":2457884,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f777e8ffc07d128dbb5c8220ada39566ef6c77c","tid":2457884,"uid":41288,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgkYEF2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgkYEF2.jpg&h=2c38c04d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:17:11.000Z","msg":"engineer + (human + 黑水)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7314e397b5f5883acc1fed361a2ad964c654e7","tid":2457884,"uid":25062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:17:34.000Z","msg":"發現外星人恐怖啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad